    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s still looking like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in absolutely pristine shape\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure driving bliss. I'm looking for a quick, smooth sale, so I've priced it to move. Come take it for a spin and see why I'm so obsessed with it!",
