    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since new. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with a professional ceramic coating and zero imperfections, rock chips, or swirl marks. Inside, the premium leather remains supple with that distinct 'new car' aroma; there is absolutely no wear on the seat bolsters, steering wheel, or interior switchgear. Mechanically, it is flawless, accompanied by a comprehensive, chronological binder of service records from authorized master technicians. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Included with the sale are both original keys, the unused factory tool kit, and all original owner\u2019s manuals. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a time-capsule specimen that looks and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 46500.0,
