    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54 platform, featuring the iconic 3.2-liter naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, mechanical engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Chassis integrity is paramount; the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the critical rod bearing service is fully documented. Finished in a concours-grade Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory depth with no imperfections. Suspension kinematics remain factory-sharp thanks to refreshed bushings and OEM dampers. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver\u2019s car for the discerning purist seeking mechanical perfection.",
